@node Tooltypes "How to edit Tooltypes"

  @{b}@{u}Tooltypes@{uu}@{ub}

  To edit tooltypes:
  -  Click once on program icon.
  -  Select INFORMATION command from Workbench ICONS pull down menu.
  -  There you'll find tooltypes lister.
@endnode



